            "text": "The Dodge Charger would remain as a B body in the fourth generation, and would move more towards the personal luxury car segment as the trend would grow to demand this in the market. Dodge would add a Magnum in 1978 to take a bigger part of that segment, and a Dodge Charger Daytona was added that had stripes the length of the car.",
