        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The styling dramatically changed for the seventh generation, becoming more angular and aggressive overall, and adopting some styling cues from the 1968-1970 Chargers. A Pentastar 3.6-liter would take duty in the base models in 2011. The 2012-2018 years would welcome the Super Bee platform, which was later changed to the wildly popular Scat Pack, using retro badging and offering better performance.",
