      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In 2015, the Charger was significantly changed and gained a more dynamic look. All models except the Charger Pursuit came with an 8-speed automatic. 2015 was also the year the extremely popular Charger Hellcat with supercharged 6.2-liter would make its debut. A widebody was introduced in 2020 to allow for a better tire/suspension package, the Redeye was also introduced for 2020.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
